rows.label: qst701905_msg0001
rows.name:
We're sorry to have kept you waiting!
We managed to get the Dragon Incense!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0002
rows.name:
Really?
Thank you so much.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0003
rows.name: Gimme! I'll make the medicine!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0004
rows.name: Do you...know how?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0005
rows.name:
Since Marena-san mentioned the
Dragon Incense, I've been studying!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0006
rows.name:
Teeco and Joey helped me get the rest
of the stuff I need, so we're good to go!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0007
rows.name: Then by all means!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0008
rows.name: Leave it to me!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0009
rows.name: Alllll done!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0010
rows.name: Drink up, Freja!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0011
rows.name: It's...not gonna be...gross again, is it?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0012
rows.name:
I added a whole bunch of sugar
this time, so it should be fine!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0013
rows.name:
Me and Laura and Laura's friends
won't let you down! Drink!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0014
rows.name: OK...let's do this.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0015
rows.name: *gulp*

rows.label: qst701905_msg0016
rows.name: Huh...?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0101
rows.name: My body feels...so light...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0102
rows.name:
No way! Is this real? What was
that medicine?!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0103
rows.name: I feel amazing!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0104
rows.name:
YESSS!!!
We did it, guys!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0105
rows.name:
I wasn't expecting it to be so
effective!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0106
rows.name: Woo hoo!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0107
rows.name:
Oh my...
Freja...my Freja...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0108
rows.name: Mum!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0109
rows.name: What a wonderful outcome.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0110
rows.name: How are you feeling, Freja?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0111
rows.name: I feel great!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0112
rows.name:
I can stand up without help!
I can even walk around!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0113
rows.name:
I think we should be able to take
Fred-san up on his offer of a spot in
the shelter now.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0114
rows.name: Yep!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0201
rows.name: My body is overflowing with energy!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0202
rows.name: I feel better than I ever have before.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0203
rows.name:
I can stand, I can walk... I feel like
I could run a marathon!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0204
rows.name:
Haha. Maybe hold off on that for
a little while.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0205
rows.name: Hehe.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0206
rows.name:
I think we should be able to take
Wotta-san up on his offer of a spot on
his evacuation ship now.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0301
rows.name:
My little girl...up and about like this...
Somebody pinch me...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0302
rows.name:
And all thanks to you, Laura, and you,
Adel. And the rest of you, of course.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0303
rows.name: How can I possibly repay you?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0304
rows.name:
That Dragon Incense was obtained
through the combined efforts of
a lot of different people.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0305
rows.name: All we did was ask them.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0306
rows.name:
So don't worry about a reward
or anything.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0307
rows.name: Quite.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0308
rows.name:
It's enough for us to see Freja
so happy.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0309
rows.name: Thank you so much!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0310
rows.name: Looks like we're all done here.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0311
rows.name:
Shin?
If you write about today in your diary,
do you think you could let me read it?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0312
rows.name: Why?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0313
rows.name:
Today was so wonderful, I want
to look back on it a little.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0314
rows.name: Why not Kagutsuchi?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0315
rows.name:
I'm afraid I have to refuse.
Why not get Minochi-san to write a book
about it?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0316
rows.name:
But-
Well, actually I was planning on writing
one anyway.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0317
rows.name:
I hope you're going to describe my
part with sufficient awesomeness.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0318
rows.name: Remind me what you did again?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0319
rows.name: Haha.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0320
rows.name:
What?! I mean, sure, I didn't have much
to do with the incense business, but
what about before that?!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0321
rows.name: What a spirited defense.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0322
rows.name: Excuse me, Prince Adel?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0323
rows.name:
I know you said you didn't need any
kind of reward, but I wanted you to
have this anyway.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0324
rows.name: What's this?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0325
rows.name:
I heard they were good for health, so
I was feeding them to Freja. Now we
have the Dragon Incense, though!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0326
rows.name:
In fact, I bought about 100 jars of the
stuff, so I have far too many left over.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0327
rows.name:
Won't you take some back
for the Lady Olgo?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0328
rows.name:
That's marvelously kind of you, thanks!
I'm sure my wife will be delighted.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0329
rows.name: Lady Olgo? Wife??

rows.label: qst701905_msg0330
rows.name: Yes. Didn't I mention?

rows.label: qst701905_msg0331
rows.name: She's back home in Aletta.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0332
rows.name:
She's pregnant. Just about due,
actually.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0333
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I cannot believe what I'm hearing!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0334
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Really??

rows.label: qst701905_msg0335
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]I didn't know that...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0336
rows.name:
You really didn't know?
I do apologize.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0337
rows.name:
So you see, I'm fighting just as much
for my family as I am for Iira.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0338
rows.name:
What are we even doing running
around saving people?!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0339
rows.name:
You need to go back to Aletta to
be with your wife!

rows.label: qst701905_msg0340
rows.name: It's fine, it's fine.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0341
rows.name:
If anything happens, Vez and Mungo
are there with her, as well as the
rest of the militia.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0342
rows.name: It'll be fine.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0343
rows.name: I'm sure it will, but...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0344
rows.name:
The best thing we can do to help her
is to make sure we put an end to Metsu
before he can cause any more ruin.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0345
rows.name: He's right. That's all we can do.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0346
rows.name: But even so...

rows.label: qst701905_msg0347
rows.name: *sigh* Yes, all right.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0348
rows.name: We have to stop Metsu.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0349
rows.name: For the sake of everyone we've met.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0350
rows.name:
For the sake of all Iirans.
And for Alst.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0351
rows.name: That's exactly right.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0352
rows.name:
I have no doubt that with such
comrades at our side, ours will
be a glorious victory.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0353
rows.name: We'll beat Metsu. Together.

rows.label: qst701905_msg0354
rows.name: Together!
